1
00:00:06,356 --> 00:00:11,252
♪Loving you is like being thrown
into a role without any preparation♪

2
00:00:11,252 --> 00:00:15,476
♪I got immersed in the act
but I lost myself♪

3
00:00:15,476 --> 00:00:18,580
♪It seems you've also sensed something♪

4
00:00:18,580 --> 00:00:21,684
♪Playing along quietly♪

5
00:00:21,684 --> 00:00:26,420
♪Loving you is like a distant wind
sweeping every corner♪

6
00:00:26,420 --> 00:00:28,948
♪Simple yet unique♪

7
00:00:28,948 --> 00:00:33,140
♪Even if I'm just a passerby, so what♪

8
00:00:33,428 --> 00:00:35,316
♪Who cares if it's worth it♪

9
00:00:35,316 --> 00:00:41,268
♪Giving you happiness
was enough, wasn't it♪

10
00:00:41,268 --> 00:00:42,388
=Taking Love as a Contract=

11
00:00:42,900 --> 00:00:46,548
=Episode 21=
(From now on, I'll be alone)

12
00:01:03,296 --> 00:01:07,027
♪Perhaps I didn't make the right choice♪

13
00:01:07,027 --> 00:01:10,757
♪I devoted myself unconditionally to it♪

14
00:01:10,757 --> 00:01:16,832
♪Now there's nothing to say
and nothing can be done♪

15
00:01:18,560 --> 00:01:22,336
♪You have complete control
over my feelings♪

16
00:01:22,336 --> 00:01:26,063
(Real Estate Title Deed)
♪I'm torn apart by conflicting emotions♪

17
00:01:26,144 --> 00:01:32,288
♪My numb heart occasionally stings,
reminding me♪

18
00:01:32,819 --> 00:01:35,669
♪What's wrong? You're silent again♪

19
00:01:35,840 --> 00:01:39,392
♪Pretending to be pathetic again♪

20
00:01:40,480 --> 00:01:44,568
♪Forgive all the sadness♪

21
00:01:44,704 --> 00:01:47,232
♪And replicate it perfectly♪

22
00:01:47,392 --> 00:01:50,176
♪That's enough. I'm tired♪

23
00:01:50,176 --> 00:01:52,288
♪Let's call it quits♪

24
00:01:52,840 --> 00:01:56,120
(Right Holder: Xia Tian)
(Now this house is back to you.)

25
00:01:57,680 --> 00:01:59,360
(I never thought)

26
00:01:59,800 --> 00:02:01,320
(that one day I would come back.)

27
00:02:03,520 --> 00:02:04,440
(Chengxuan,)

28
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:06,960
(thank you.)

29
00:02:07,328 --> 00:02:11,712
♪Hold back the tears
when turning around♪

30
00:02:11,840 --> 00:02:17,588
♪You say you will still miss me.
You just won't love me anymore♪

31
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:22,120
(Excuse me.)

32
00:02:22,760 --> 00:02:25,440
(Spicy intestine noodles, please.)

33
00:02:26,440 --> 00:02:27,880
I'll take pig trotter noodles.

34
00:02:27,880 --> 00:02:28,680
No problem.

35
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:32,120
Garlic and noodles,

36
00:02:32,720 --> 00:02:33,920
a perfect match.

37
00:02:39,160 --> 00:02:40,120
(You better leave.)

38
00:02:41,200 --> 00:02:42,600
(From now on,)

39
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:44,520
(our cooperation)

40
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:46,320
(is over.)

41
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:47,680
Grandma,

42
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:52,280
from now on, I'll be alone.

43
00:02:52,832 --> 00:02:55,424
♪What's wrong? You're silent again♪

44
00:02:56,600 --> 00:02:58,160
I deserve to be alone.

45
00:03:00,416 --> 00:03:04,384
♪Forgive all the sadness♪

46
00:03:04,669 --> 00:03:07,296
♪And replicate it perfectly♪

47
00:03:07,296 --> 00:03:10,144
♪That's enough. I'm tired♪

48
00:03:10,144 --> 00:03:12,416
♪Let's call it quits♪

49
00:03:12,416 --> 00:03:16,375
♪You cried and laughed,
but in the end, you left♪

50
00:03:16,608 --> 00:03:19,904
♪I will feel sad and lonely too♪

51
00:03:19,936 --> 00:03:22,496
♪You know it♪

52
00:03:22,496 --> 00:03:25,440
♪Don't wait anymore. Forget our past♪

53
00:03:25,440 --> 00:03:27,584
♪Remember to live well♪

54
00:03:27,584 --> 00:03:31,667
♪Hold back the tears
when turning around♪

55
00:03:31,872 --> 00:03:37,024
♪You say you will still miss me.
You just won't love me anymore♪

56
00:03:50,480 --> 00:03:51,520
Happy housewarming.

57
00:03:55,440 --> 00:03:56,320
Don't drink too much.

58
00:03:56,840 --> 00:03:57,760
We need to work tomorrow.

59
00:03:58,600 --> 00:04:00,880
You're so eager to devote yourself
to that old man?

60
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:03,480
Now that's your company.

61
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:06,120
I don't want that company.

62
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:08,600
Dealing with a pile of things every day

63
00:04:08,600 --> 00:04:10,000
as a CEO

64
00:04:11,320 --> 00:04:13,080
will make me old.

65
00:04:14,480 --> 00:04:15,680
You can hand it over to me.

66
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:19,880
Then who will keep me company?

67
00:04:20,320 --> 00:04:21,480
You mean...?

68
00:04:24,440 --> 00:04:26,320
I've already planned
to sell the company.

69
00:04:27,360 --> 00:04:28,680
With that money,

70
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:30,360
we can go far away

71
00:04:30,880 --> 00:04:32,480
and live a happy life. Isn't it good?

72
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:36,200
Such a big company.

73
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:38,040
Who can take it over?

74
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:40,080
I've already found someone.

75
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:41,240
It's him.

76
00:04:42,520 --> 00:04:43,320
Stephen.

77
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:48,240
Just take a look.

78
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:57,120
Take a look.

79
00:05:03,360 --> 00:05:04,720
Grandpa suddenly fell unconscious.

80
00:05:05,480 --> 00:05:06,680
The company's stock price plummeted.

81
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:10,080
Selling it now

82
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:12,280
would mean a big loss.

83
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:14,320
What can I do about it?

84
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:16,120
There's no other way now

85
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:17,480
to stimulate the stock price.

86
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:20,640
Not even our engagement?

87
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:30,000
You mean

88
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:31,720
we should get married.

89
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:33,040
And this strong alliance

90
00:05:33,240 --> 00:05:35,360
will surely lead

91
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:37,360
the group's stock price to rise.

92
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:41,280
How can you be so clever?

93
00:05:53,400 --> 00:05:54,960
How do you think

94
00:05:56,760 --> 00:05:58,400
we should celebrate?

95
00:06:11,280 --> 00:06:12,520
Let's talk about it later.

96
00:06:14,800 --> 00:06:15,880
You just moved in today.

97
00:06:16,200 --> 00:06:17,280
Have a good rest.

98
00:06:18,200 --> 00:06:20,720
I'll go and follow up
on the engagement ceremony.

99
00:06:31,760 --> 00:06:32,800
Be good.

100
00:06:40,280 --> 00:06:40,880
Good.

101
00:06:45,080 --> 00:06:45,680
I'm off.

102
00:07:28,896 --> 00:07:33,248
♪I've been through
several winters alone♪

103
00:07:34,368 --> 00:07:38,579
♪Sorry, I didn't end up with you♪

104
00:07:39,776 --> 00:07:45,888
♪From infatuation to heartache,
it's also a kind of bravery♪

105
00:07:50,624 --> 00:07:55,520
♪Holding back the tears,
I watch you and her together♪

106
00:07:56,000 --> 00:08:00,640
♪Smiling at you,
I say I'll be a mere spectator♪

107
00:08:04,240 --> 00:08:06,400
I really hope every time you feel down,

108
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:09,240
I can be the one by your side.

109
00:08:11,104 --> 00:08:16,611
♪From now on,
I'll face the rain and wind alone♪

110
00:08:16,611 --> 00:08:21,997
♪I watch you fall for her
and ache for her♪

111
00:08:22,112 --> 00:08:24,800
♪I'm just a spectator♪

112
00:08:25,440 --> 00:08:32,703
♪With no right to take part in
the rest of your life♪

113
00:08:32,960 --> 00:08:38,330
♪I'll dream and worry alone♪

114
00:08:38,400 --> 00:08:43,962
♪I watch her by your side♪

115
00:08:43,962 --> 00:08:47,232
♪I can only be a spectator♪

116
00:08:47,328 --> 00:08:52,256
♪Staying far from your life♪

117
00:08:53,920 --> 00:08:55,160
Ji Chengxuan,

118
00:08:56,040 --> 00:08:57,720
you lousy man.

119
00:09:00,920 --> 00:09:02,160
When did actors suddenly start

120
00:09:02,160 --> 00:09:04,160
expecting such lofty morals?

121
00:09:05,728 --> 00:09:08,780
♪I'm just a spectator♪

122
00:09:08,928 --> 00:09:16,394
♪With no right to take part in
the rest of your life♪

123
00:09:16,640 --> 00:09:22,141
♪I'll dream and worry alone♪

124
00:09:22,141 --> 00:09:27,456
♪I watch her by your side♪

125
00:09:27,584 --> 00:09:30,912
♪I can only be a spectator♪

126
00:09:30,912 --> 00:09:35,366
♪Staying far from your life♪

127
00:09:41,800 --> 00:09:42,800
Why are you here?

128
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:45,000
Let me explain.

129
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:49,040
I agreed with Shen Yueran
for two reasons.

130
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:51,440
One is to protect the company.

131
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:53,440
The other is to find out the real reason

132
00:09:53,440 --> 00:09:54,320
behind Grandpa's illness.

133
00:09:57,440 --> 00:09:59,160
You can't be so foolish
that you didn't realize it?

134
00:10:00,760 --> 00:10:02,520
Do you think I'll trust you again?

135
00:10:09,800 --> 00:10:11,440
We've cooperated so many times,

136
00:10:12,920 --> 00:10:15,000
but you don't have
an ounce of trust in me?

137
00:10:34,480 --> 00:10:36,840
You went too far with your words today.

138
00:10:42,120 --> 00:10:43,120
You said it.

139
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:45,640
The stronger the performance,

140
00:10:46,520 --> 00:10:48,000
the more it needs to maintain suspense.

141
00:11:09,400 --> 00:11:10,480
Why are you laughing?

142
00:11:11,880 --> 00:11:12,920
What's so funny?

143
00:11:19,440 --> 00:11:20,480
Xia Tian,

144
00:11:23,040 --> 00:11:24,640
you're really too gullible.

145
00:11:26,080 --> 00:11:27,400
Who do you think you are?

146
00:11:28,800 --> 00:11:31,640
Do you really think
you're that charming?

147
00:11:32,640 --> 00:11:34,680
Where does your confidence come from?

148
00:11:40,120 --> 00:11:40,920
Wait.

149
00:11:42,840 --> 00:11:44,120
Make it clear.

150
00:11:46,360 --> 00:11:47,960
Rather than being around a useless

151
00:11:47,960 --> 00:11:49,320
and fake heiress each day,

152
00:11:51,080 --> 00:11:52,400
I might as well be

153
00:11:53,480 --> 00:11:56,160
with a real one.

154
00:11:57,680 --> 00:11:58,480
Xia Tian,

155
00:11:59,240 --> 00:12:00,680
compared with He's Group,

156
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:03,240
you are nothing.

157
00:12:07,640 --> 00:12:08,680
Chengxuan,

158
00:12:09,600 --> 00:12:10,680
you wouldn't...

159
00:13:00,915 --> 00:13:03,617
♪Unconsciously, I look at you♪

160
00:13:03,846 --> 00:13:06,323
♪Your eyes are filled with stars♪

161
00:13:06,578 --> 00:13:09,459
♪With only my reflection♪

162
00:13:12,424 --> 00:13:14,862
♪The warm sea breeze kisses you♪

163
00:13:14,862 --> 00:13:17,651
♪My longing makes me hold my breath♪

164
00:13:17,651 --> 00:13:21,587
♪My mind is so certain♪

165
00:13:22,387 --> 00:13:26,805
♪This love silently♪

166
00:13:28,077 --> 00:13:32,211
♪Orbits the trajectory of stars♪

167
00:13:33,779 --> 00:13:40,755
♪Hidden in the breath,
leaked through the eyes♪

168
00:13:44,531 --> 00:13:49,267
♪Listen, the silent heart
awakens for you♪

169
00:13:50,227 --> 00:13:55,219
♪I nearly missed the chance
to embrace you♪

170
00:13:55,583 --> 00:13:58,355
♪Lies can't hide true feelings♪

171
00:13:58,771 --> 00:14:00,766
♪Listen♪
